-c***begin prologue  dqawo
-c***date written   800101   (yymmdd)
-c***revision date  830518   (yymmdd)
-c***category no.  h2a2a1
-c***keywords  automatic integrator, special-purpose,
-c             integrand with oscillatory cos or sin factor,
